### 01. 내 업무 전체 조회 (기본)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/my/tasks?workspacePublicId={{workspacePublicId}}&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 02. 내 업무 조회 (상태 필터)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/my/tasks?workspacePublicId={{workspacePublicId}}&status=TODO&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 03. 내 업무 조회 (우선순위 필터)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/my/tasks?workspacePublicId={{workspacePublicId}}&priority=URGENT&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 04. 내 업무 조회 (마감일 범위 필터)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/my/tasks?workspacePublicId={{workspacePublicId}}&dueDateFrom=2026-05-01&dueDateTo=2026-05-31&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 05. 내 업무 조회 (복합 필터 - 인덱스 최적화 검증용)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/my/tasks?workspacePublicId={{workspacePublicId}}&status=IN_PROGRESS&priority=HIGH&dueDateFrom=2026-04-29&dueDateTo=2026-06-30&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}